      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"2. BUSH BOODIE has an excellent record here having never missed the placings in three starts, including two wins. Placed last time (19.11) at this track in a Restricted WIN, finishing third and beaten 0.8 lengths. Looks a key chance on best form. 3. GEMSTONE JASPER continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at his last four runs. Last time finished 2nd on April 8 over 352m at Q Lakeside behind Regal Saint beaten 2.5 lengths (19.84) in a Grade 5. Expected to feature. 1. BRABAZON has been out of the placings at her last couple but on the winners' heels when placing three back (16.91) in a Grade 5 at this track. Well placed here and should do much better. 6. BONEY MALONEY can run a bold race on best form.\",\"runners\":[2,3,1,6],\"exclusive\":false}",
